          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-10M1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HREE merry Lads you own we are;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-2" n="2">'Tis very true, and free from Care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-3" n="3">But envious we cannot bear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-4" n="4">«LD»believe, Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-5" n="5">For were all Forms of Beauty thine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-6" n="6">Were you like <hi rend="italics">Nireus</hi>, soft and fine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-7" n="7">We shou'd not in the least repine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-8" n="8">«LD»or grieve, Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-9" n="9">Then know from us, most beauteous <hi rend="italics">Dan</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-10" n="10">That Roughness best becomes a Man;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-11" n="11">'Tis Women should be pale and wan,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-12" n="12">«LD»and taper.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-13" n="13">And all your trifling Beaux and Fops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-14" n="14">Who comb their Brows and sleek their Chops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-15" n="15">Are but the Offspring of Toy-shops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-16" n="16">«LD»meer Vapour.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-17" n="17">We know your Morning Hours you pass</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-18" n="18">To cull and gather out a Face;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-19" n="19">Is this the Way you take your Glass?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-20" n="20">«LD»forbear it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-21" n="21">Those Loads of Paint upon your Toilet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-22" n="22">Will never mend your Face, but spoil it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-23" n="23">It looks as if you did par-boil it.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-24" n="24">«LD»Drink Claret.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-25" n="25">Your Cheeks, by sleeking, are so lean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-26" n="26">That they're like <hi rend="italics">Cynthia</hi> in the Wain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-27" n="27">Or Breast of Goose when 'tis pick'd clean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-28" n="28">«LD»or Pullet.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-29" n="29">See, what by drinking you have done,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-30" n="30">You've made your Phiz a Skeleton,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-31" n="31">From the long Distance of your Crown,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-10M1-line-32" n="32">«LD»t'your Gullet!</l>
          </lg>
